dct_title_s: An international travel map, Belize, Scale 1:350,000
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depths shown by contours. Legend in English and Spanish Panel Title Includes text, statistical data, and ancillary map of Half Moon Cay Natural Monument Reservation. Panel includes "243" in upper right corner. International Travel Maps (Firm) International Travel Maps and Books (ITMB) Publishing Ltd.
